data.description: Welcome home to this charming ranch in the Peeks Crossing neighborhood in Senoia! Conveniently located just 5 minutes from all of the great restaurants and shops on Main Street. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch on a large corner lot is the perfect place to call home. Private backyard. Side entry garage. Living room with fireplace & vaulted ceiling. Open floorplan with family room opening to kitchen. Great for entertaining. Access to backyard via sliding glass doors in kitchen. Stainless steel appliances. Come see this home today!
